/* This skin is designed to help make the site easier to read without having to apply an actual dyslexia font. It creates more space in-between letters, words, lines, and paragraphs.
I'm interested in feedback from people using it if you have anything you'd like changed!
I took inspiration from this article: https://www.smashingmagazine.com/2021/11/dyslexia-friendly-mode-website/ */

